dct_title_s: Plan of Jaffa / reproduced by the Survey of Egypt.
dct_description_sm: Map shows German colony (Walhalla Quarter); Muslim, Catholic, Armenian, and Coptic cemeteries; Coptic; Armenian, and Greek Orthodox, Russian churches; customs port of entry;  roads; cultivated areas. "June 1918. (264)." Stamp on lower right margin: "Survey of Palestine. Map archives; section Z; cupboard no. 1; folio 5; map no. 15" Map is a photocopy reproduction dated 11. 10. 2007 from the Israel Mapping Center.
